original_title: 青春って目がクラクラ回るものなんですね！！ 桜井千春 SOD専属 AVデビュー
overview: Nice to meet everyone. This is Chiharu Sakurai. I've always been shy and withdrawn, and I decided to make my AV debut, thinking that if I entered this kind of world, I would be different from myself. The first shoot was embarrassing and full of things I didn't understand ... My head turned white. Thank you for your support m (__) m!
title: Youth Is So Dazzling!! Chiharu Sakurai SOD Actress Porn Debut
